 _______________________________________________________________________
 
 Mandriva Linux Security Advisory                         MDVSA-2008:073
 http://www.mandriva.com/security/
 _______________________________________________________________________
 
 Package : perl-Net-DNS
 Date    : March 20, 2008
 Affected: 2007.0, 2007.1, 2008.0, Corporate 3.0, Corporate 4.0
 _______________________________________________________________________
 
 Problem Description:
 
 A vulnerability in the Net::DNS perl module was found that could
 allow remote attackers to cause a denial of service via a crafted
 DNS response.
 
 The updated packages have been patched to correct this issue.
 _______________________________________________________________________

 References:
 
 http://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2007-6341
 _______________________________________________________________________
 
